    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 4. Confirmation + Reminder Sequence\nSend a confirmation right away, then use `Wait` nodes to fire a 24-hour-before reminder, a 30-minute-before reminder, and a post-meeting follow-up — all from this one execution. If a resume time has already passed (e.g. a same-day booking), the Wait node just resumes immediately.",
